					<header class="rail-article-author">
  <h2 class="rail-article-brand-title">Joe Klein</h2>
  <img class="rail-article-author-photo" src="http://i0.wp.com/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2014/01/voss-timeheadshots47final.jpg?crop=1003px%2C79px%2C3236px%2C3236px&amp;resize=100%2C100" />
  <p class="rail-article-summary-paragraph">Joe Klein is TIME's political columnist and author of six books, most recently <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Politics-Lost-Politicians-Courageous-Interested/dp/0767916018"><i>Politics Lost</i></a>. His weekly TIME column, "In the Arena," covers national and international affairs. In 2004 he won the National Headliner Award for best magazine column.</p>
