    	     <a class="time-icons time-icons-tw social-link-tw popup" href="#" data-href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5HMd-f5ZN&text=Joe%20Klein%20on%20working%20with%20Mike%20Nichols&via=TIMECulture" data-event="tweet-lwr" title="Click to Tweet this article"></a>
    	     <a class="time-icons time-icons-mail social-link social-link-mail" href="mailto:?subject=Remembering%20Mike%20Nichols%3A%20%E2%80%98He%20Was%20Relentlessly%20Gracious%2C%20Clever%20and%20Generous%E2%80%99%20%7C%20TIME&body=Remembering%20Mike%20Nichols%3A%20%E2%80%98He%20Was%20Relentlessly%20Gracious%2C%20Clever%20and%20Generous%E2%80%99%0A%0AThe%20author%20of%20the%20book%20that%20inspired%20one%20of%20Nichols%27%20most%20memorable%20films%20remembers%20the%20director%2C%20who%20died%20Nov.%2020%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3597971%2Fmike-nichols-primary-colors-joe-kline%2F" data-event="email-lwr" title="Click to Email this article"></a>
