    	     <a class="time-icons time-icons-mail social-link social-link-mail" href="mailto:?subject=Obama%E2%80%99s%20Leadership%20Shortage%20%7C%20TIME&body=Obama%E2%80%99s%20Leadership%20Shortage%0A%0AHis%20policies%20are%20fine.%20But%20the%20President%20is%20often%20a%20prisoner%20of%20his%20instincts%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3512660%2Fbarack-obamas-leadership-shortage%2F" data-event="email-lwr" title="Click to Email this article"></a>
    	</div>
        <div id="micro-comments-wrapper">
         	<a href="#" class="time-icons time-icons-comment livefyre-commentcount toggle-comments" data-event="comment-lwr" data-lf-site-id="314099" data-lf-article-id="3512660" data-url="http://time.com/3512660/barack-obamas-leadership-shortage/" data-title="Obama’s Leadership Shortage" title="Click to view and post comments">0</a>
