ecretary of the Navy under Ronald Reagan. His one term in the Senate was protean, with Webb focusing on issues as diverse as the reestablishment of relations with Burma, and prison reform, and the new GI bill for Iraq-Afghanistan veterans.<\/p>\n<p>He will be a refreshing presence on the campaign trail. He doesn&#8217;t talk like a politician. He can be blunt and combative. He has taken strong populist economic stands and was a strong opponent of the war in Iraq. In fact, Webb goes in strong whenever he takes a stand. He&#8217;ll certainly be fun to watch during debates (he was a boxer at Annapolis).<\/p>\n<p>You&#8217;d have to call him a longshot, of course. But I suspect he&#8217;ll be one of those long shots who have the power to shape a campaign with new ideas and sharp arguments. He will certainly cause Clinton some populist agita, should she run.<\/p>\n<aside class=\"right-rail-module rr-share\" data-name=\"rr-share\"><span class=\"social-links\">\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-mail social-link-mail\" href=\"mailto:?subject=Jim%20Webb%20is%20Running%20%7C%20TIME&body=Jim%20Webb%20is%20Running%0A%0AHe%27s%20a%20long%20shot%2C%20but%20could%20give%20Hillary%20heartburn%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3598255%2Fjim-webb-is-running%2F\" data-event=\"email\" title=\"Click to Email this article\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-fb social-link-fb popup\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/sharer\/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3598255%2Fjim-webb-is-running%2F\" data-event=\"fb-share\" title=\"Click to post this article to Facebook\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-tw social-link-tw popup\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/intent\/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp5HMd-f64n&text=Former%20Virginia%20senator%20Jim%20Webb%20is%20officially%20running%20for%20president.&via=TIMEPolitics\" data-event=\"tweet\" title=\"Click to Tweet this article\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-linkedin social-link-linkedin popup\" 